| doi = 10.2337/dc08-0349
| url =
| pmc = 2494626
}}</ref>

A [[ketogenic diet]] impairs the ability of the kidney to excrete uric acid, due to competition for transport between uric acid and [[ketone]]s.<ref name="pmid488876">{{cite journal
