}}</ref>

==Dalmatian dogs==
In [[Dalmatian (dog)|Dalmatian dogs]], a lack of [[uricase]] (a genetic trait [[Fixation (population genetics)|fixed]] in this breed) contributes to hyperuricemia and corresponding [[hyperuricosuria]].
